com.vk.sdk.api.model

Class VKApiModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vk.sdk.api.model.VKApiModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    VKApiChat, VKApiCity, VKApiComment, VKApiCommunityFull.Contact, VKApiCommunityFull.Link, VKApiCountry, VKApiMessage, VKApiOwner, VKApiPhotoSize, VKApiPlace, VKApiPoll.Answer, VKApiSchool, VKApiUniversity, VKApiUserFull.Relative, VKAttachments.VKApiAttachment, VKList, VKWallPostResult

    public abstract class VKApiModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Root class for all VK models. Any VK model supports Parcelable interface so you can pass it as extra. VK model is also allows you to store some object inside as a tag. These objects are retained by hard links, and never will be saved during parcelization.
